  "text": "We also compare the performance of SVMs to that of the C4.5 decision tree algorithm, another classification algorithm that was shown to have good device classification results by Kunze et al. [CITATION_1] . When the same set of features are used, our regularized kernel method shows better generalization capability, as it captures the similarity between the training and test data more effectively. As in [CITATION_2] , we use WEKA [CITATION_3] for the decision tree implementation.",
